{"tid":1075884,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"深宵廚房 - Buffalo Wings 水牛城雞翼","createTime":"2019-03-24T12:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T12:40:01.000Z","uid":55640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9b852ff56b65bf20c54609406eb5b69db16db3c4","tid":1075884,"uid":55640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:40:01.000Z","msg":"平時去酒吧都好鍾意叫水牛城雞翼配啤酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一路飲酒 一路食雞翼 真係爽到無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tkf44GF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftkf44GF.jpg&h=24829beb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日同大家分享係屋企都可以享受嘅世界級享受！<br />\nBuffalo Wings 材料 <br />\n雞中翼，茄汁，牛油，西式辣椒汁，粟粉/炸粉，糖， 蒜鹽，黑胡椒，西芹，紅蘿蔔，藍芝士醬/乳酪 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zv1sh1L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZv1sh1L.jpg&h=d7970fa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先將雞翼洗乾淨，瀝乾，然後用蒜鹽、黑胡椒、糖醃大約10至15分鐘。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TKPQ0fo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTKPQ0fo.jpg&h=fa574ebf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將醃好的雞翼平均地鋪上一層薄薄嘅粟粉/炸粉，然後可以放落去預熱好咗嘅油鑊，每邊炸大約3分鐘，顏色變成金黃、浮起便代表雞翼已經熟咗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xg82Rm9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXg82Rm9.jpg&h=da007782&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水牛城雞翼嘅汁係用大約200g嘅牛油，用慢火煮溶。然之後加入適量嘅茄汁、西式辣椒汁、少量的鹽同埋糖將佢煮到濃稠即可。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/frkTX2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfrkTX2e.jpg&h=58a15f1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將炸好嘅雞翼放落醬汁裏面翻滾兜勻就可以上碟。 最後配以切好咗嘅西芹同埋紅蘿蔔條，側邊放少少藍芝士醬或乳酪就可以上枱啦。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBOY880.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBOY880.jpg&h=d50bfa50&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}